      "title": "\"Ezekiel’s Topography of the (Un-)Heroic Dead in Ezekiel 32:17–32\" by Brian R. Doak",
      "domain": "digitalcommons.georgefox.edu",
      "category": "crawled",
      "credibilityTier": "reputable-reference",
